* '''Grupo Catalana Occidente S.A.'''
Grupo Catalana Occidente S.A.直接或间接地成为许多保险公司的母公司。GCO在巴塞罗那<ref>{{Cite web|title=Barcelona|url=http://www.borsabcn.es/ing/aspx/Empresas/FichaValor.aspx?ISIN=ES0116920333&ClvEmis=16920|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116085039/https://www.borsabcn.es/ing/aspx/Empresas/FichaValor.aspx?ISIN=ES0116920333&ClvEmis=16920|dead-url=no}}</ref>和马德里证券交易所上市<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bolsamadrid.es/ing/aspx/Empresas/FichaValor.aspx?ISIN=ES0116920333&ClvEmis=16920|title=Bolsa de Madrid|accessdate=2017-08-14|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128163436/https://www.bolsamadrid.es/ing/aspx/Empresas/FichaValor.aspx?ISIN=ES0116920333&ClvEmis=16920|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在Atradius N.V.中持有83.20的股份，其中直接持有35.77%，通过Grupo CyC控股公司间接持有47.43%<ref>{{Cite web|title=安卓2020年报|url=https://group.atradius.com/about-us/annual-reports.html|access-date=2017-02-15|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329150418/https://group.atradius.com/about-us/annual-reports.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''Grupo Crédito y Caución S.L. (Grupo CyC)'''
